body.name: TISHLED Typewriter Keyboard Wireless 2.4GHz/Bluetooth/USB-C Wired Rechargeable Membrane Gaming Keyboard Linear Mechanical-Feel Switch Compact 85-Key Retro Round Keycaps for Multi-Device, Matcha Green
deliveryMessages: Or fastest delivery Thursday, February 15. Order within 1 hr 18 mins
features: [Tri-Mode Connection] - Powerful 3-mode connection supports Wireless 2.4GHz/Bluetooth 5.0/USB-C Wired. You can connect up to 2 bluetooth devices, 1 wireless 2.4GHz device and 1 wired device. Connect and switch devices easily with Fn+1~4. Compatible with Win, MacOS, IOS and Android systems. Switch the system by pressing Fn+Q/W/E/R according to the connected device. Support PC, Mac, smartphone, ipad and tablet.

[Retro Aesthetic Typewriter Style Keyboard] - The typewriter keyboard is a fusion of retro style and modern design. Cute colorful round keycaps and advanced connection technology make typing more comfortable and enjoyable.

[Membrane Keys (Not Mechanical Keys)] - Linear mechanical feeling switch, medium resistance and fast response, provide a comfortable and satisfying typing experience. Great for both office work and gaming.

[Rechargeable & Energy-Saving] - The keyboard has a 300mAh lithium battery, with low-power chip and energy-saving technology, it can last between 7-15 days, depending on usage. The keyboard goes to Hibernation Mode in 5 seconds of sitting idle to save battery, any key to wake up.

[Ergonomic & Compact Design] - The ergonomic keyboard includes adjustable feet alleviate pressure on your wrist from typing at an elevated angle. 85-key compact design, lightweight and portable(12.6*5.3*1.3in, 1.03lb). It frees up workspace on your desk without sacrificing performance and comfort during your work.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just as pictured! MUCH better than other aesthetic keyboards I’ve seen out there
reviews.reviewText: Very cute, goes with my aesthetic. I love the clicky sounds; it’s very satisfying. I love that it’s rechargeable! MUCH better than the UBOIT brand that doesn’t even toggle to Mac operating systems. The only complaint I have so far is that it’s not very ergonomic as my fingers will hurt after typing for a long time.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Pretty, but zero typewriter feel to it
reviews.reviewText: While this is an adorable keyboard (the colors are pretty and the style of it is nice), I don't feel it's entirely as advertised. The title says that it's a typewriter keyboard and then the description says the keys aren't mechanical. I assumed, wrongly, that the keyboard would still have a typewriter feel and click to the keys, due to other wording in the description. It's the only reason I bought it. So if you're looking for anything even *resembling* a typewriter, this isn't it. I don't feel that word should be in the description.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Charge before use
reviews.reviewText: It’s a great keyboard so far just make sure your charge it with the USB cable before hand.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Can't operate without being plugged in
reviews.reviewText: The keyboard was great for typing, had a good feel. However, there is no space to insert a battery and it doesn't work unless it is plugged in all the time.

Super sencillo de emparejar y puedes conectarlo al mismo tiempo a dos dispositivos. Las teclas son cómodas. Se carga con un cable tipo C, lo que es genial. Y llegó antes de la fecha estimada de entrega en caja y bien protegido. Sin duda la volvería a comprar.
